'''格雷格·阿博特'''（Greg Abbott；{{bd|1957年|11月13日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物<ref name="WashPostReid10302014">{{cite news |last=Wilson |first=Reid |date=2014-10-30 |title=The likely next governor of Texas is full of Lone Star swagger. Don’t be surprised if he runs for president. |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/govbeat/wp/2014/10/30/the-likely-next-governor-of-texas-is-full-of-lone-star-swagger-dont-be-surprised-if-he-runs-for-president/ |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |location=[[Washington,_D.C.|Washington, D.C.]] |accessdate=2014-10-31 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310005154/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/govbeat/wp/2014/10/30/the-likely-next-governor-of-texas-is-full-of-lone-star-swagger-dont-be-surprised-if-he-runs-for-president/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://votesmart.org/candidate/biography/50168/greg-abbott |title=Attorney General Greg Abbott's Biography - Project Vote Smart |publisher=Votesmart.org |date=1957-11-13 |accessdate=2013-10-14 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007184424/http://votesmart.org/candidate/biography/50168/greg-abbott |dead-url=no }}</ref>。格雷格·阿博特自2015年開始擔任第48任德克薩斯州州長。格雷格·阿博特的黨籍是[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]。阿博特在擔任州長之前曾是德州總檢察長，他是德州自重建時期以來第二位共和黨籍的總檢察長。他是自1967年乔治·华莱士（George Wallace）卸任以来美国所有州中第一位永久使用轮椅的州长。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Why is Governor Greg Abbott in a Wheelchair?|url=https://www.gregabbott.com/why-governor-greg-abbott-wheelchair/|accessdate=2020-04-06|work=Greg Abbott|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200430150103/https://www.gregabbott.com/why-governor-greg-abbott-wheelchair/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

1984年的一个午后，阿博特在[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]橡树河社区慢跑时，被一棵橡树砸伤，从此留下残疾。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2018/05/18/why-texas-gov-greg-abbott-uses-a-wheelchair/ |title=Why Texas Gov. Greg Abbott uses a wheelchair |date=2018-05-18 |work=The Dallas Morning News |accessdate=2020-07-11 |language=en |archive-date=2020-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711102343/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2018/05/18/why-texas-gov-greg-abbott-uses-a-wheelchair/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在擔任總檢察長之前，阿博特是[[德克薩斯州最高法院|德克薩斯州最高法院]]法官，他最初是在1995年由时任州长[[小布什|小布什]]（George W. Bush）任命的。在2005年[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]称为{{le|范奥登诉佩里案|Van Orden v. Perry}}中，他成功地主张德克萨斯州有权在奥斯汀的德克萨斯州议会大厦面前展示十诫''。''

[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]期間，格雷格·阿博特反對强制戴口罩制度。2021年8月18日，格雷格·阿博特感染新冠病毒<ref>{{cite news |title=美国反对强制戴口罩制度的得州州长感染新冠病毒 |url=https://sputniknews.cn/politics/202108181034298661/ |accessdate=2021-08-18 |archive-date=2021-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123042519/https://sputniknews.cn/politics/202108181034298661/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
